dct_title_s: Liberty Thoroughfare and properties along Mordecai Island, Little Egg Harbor Bay
dct_description_sm: This is a map of property lots on Mordecai Island The property lots are either blacked out, blank, numbered, or depict the outline of the buildings located on them. The roads surrounding the blocks are also labelled.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
